<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>POWER STEERING GEAR: SHEPPARD M-SERIES - IDENTIFICATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="x0501507" svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="4">
        <title>IDENTIFICATION</title>
        <para>A number is cast into the steering gear housing (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0501502">Figure 2</hotlnk>) and identifies the basic family the steering gear belongs to.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0501502" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg05/G0500202.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px"/>
            <caption>Figure 2. Identification Number Cast Into Steering Gear Housing</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>Stamped letters and numbers on an exposed machined surface of the housing opposite the mounting side
            identifies the gear specification (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0501503">Figure 3</hotlnk>); see gear P/N chart. In the example, the complete
            identification is Model M-100PADIAI. Cast number M-100 (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0501504">Figure 4</hotlnk>) would refer to the M-Series steering gear family.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0501503" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg05/G0501503.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="352px"
                     scalefitheight="312px"/>
            <caption>Figure 3. Gear Part Number Chart</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="f0501504" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg05/G0500203.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                     scalefitheight="312px"/>
            <caption>Figure 4. Gear Specification Number</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>A serial number is also assigned to each steering gear and is interpreted in
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0501505">Figure 5</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0501505" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg05/G0501505.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="328px"
                     scalefitheight="312px"/>
            <caption>Figure 5. Serial Number System</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
